author: veithen
msg: Slightly changed the behavior of the LLOM implementation of OMElement#cloneOMElement(). It was creating an OMDocument as the parent of the clone, but this seems to be accidental rather than intentional. DOOM's implementation doesn't create this OMDocument and the clone is orphaned.
